{"tid":503544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"平安夜女朋友定老母","createTime":"2017-12-19T03:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T07:58:32.000Z","uid":28450,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"aca470c7623c65c513b910e197c5708b6eb3d7b8","tid":503544,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"話說女朋友係做空姐，本身佢話聖誕果幾日要飛<br />\n咁好啦我就同我屋企人約左24號食聖誕大餐<br />\nBook哂buffet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然間條女話轉左更唔洗飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要同我去食飯倒數<br />\n正常情況梗係join埋一起食<br />\n問題係條女不嬲唔like同我屋企人食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求救"},{"pid":"4066bf91209213decb6ae3ca27ea139d6cb9b709","tid":503544,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"中出即飛"},{"pid":"8cb6a66b86348da58ec7c9344ebd110a9a9c6744","tid":503544,"uid":96533,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"梗係屋企人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6417ebfb29f6c4e27efdb4b375433267c75749","tid":503544,"uid":2772,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"「問題係條女不嬲唔like同我屋企人食飯」<br />\n條女痴撚線 幾時輪到佢出聲"},{"pid":"b8f05e5ee656ad00f301d55b76fedf022683b188","tid":503544,"uid":32298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"老母啦"},{"pid":"4dc29765b904c59efa49bbdd8ffdf2372875702a","tid":503544,"uid":28493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"你係咪男人黎？咁都要問？仲有你聖誕倒乜春野數？你唔識搵第日同條女食？"},{"pid":"2036cd065b69